SetInCountry: Egypt
Category: The last thing I expected
AuthorName: Pounamu Soochoon
AuthorCountry: New Zealand
Text: My name is Pounamu, which is a New Zealand natural gem stone. Ironic as I'll
  probably be sitting on the plane with a name meaning 'stone' or treasure'. I haven't
  traveled many places I love to write novels and I think this would be a fantastic
  thing to experience.
